European Stocks Fall as Carmakers, Technology Shares Slide; Opap Advances

-- B y   A n d r e w   R u m m e r
-- 
2011-04-14T07:05:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-14/european-stocks-fall-as-carmakers-technology-shares-slide-opap-advances.html
European stocks declined for the
third time in four days as automakers and technology companies
retreated. The Stoxx Europe 600 Index lost 0.3 percent to 277.4
at 8:04 a.m. in  London .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
